    "description": "大家好！我们是二人独立开发团队Mechland！这是我们开发的全新横板类魂游戏《黑塔战记》！<br><br>我们开发这款游戏的初衷是想做一款“手残魂”。我们简化了基本操作，只保留了攻击和翻滚，连行走都给玩家省去了。我们把攻击和弹反键合二为一，玩家只要在恰当的时候按下攻击键，就能轻松获得攻防一体化的流畅战斗体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/b75b92eea1504cad2a7bd4201c84bfcc.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/b75b92eea1504cad2a7bd4201c84bfcc.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/b75b92eea1504cad2a7bd4201c84bfcc.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，你所能够做的远不仅此。你可以在冒险的途中学到各式各样的剑术和魔法，用来扩充你的战斗手段。当你遇到难缠的战斗时，善用你的技能把，这会让你的征程变得更加顺利！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/3faabac5e68adc72d77760686663aa88.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/3faabac5e68adc72d77760686663aa88.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/3faabac5e68adc72d77760686663aa88.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/ad304ebc435019f454e97a60d069aaa6.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/ad304ebc435019f454e97a60d069aaa6.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/ad304ebc435019f454e97a60d069aaa6.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>除此之外，你还可以获得各种独特的饰品装备。利用特定技能和装备来构筑自己的角色，形成自己的战斗风格，将让你在冒险中得心应手。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/9a8dce8d0fb7dfcc198dd14a1b86514c.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/9a8dce8d0fb7dfcc198dd14a1b86514c.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/9a8dce8d0fb7dfcc198dd14a1b86514c.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过不断地探索黑塔，你会结交各色各样的NPC。聆听他们的诉求吧，你会在得到他们帮助的同时，一步一步了解发生在黑塔之中的阴暗故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/85fda9bd3153b50d9bd4067083b3efad.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/85fda9bd3153b50d9bd4067083b3efad.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/85fda9bd3153b50d9bd4067083b3efad.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当然，最大的挑战莫过于高难度的boss。他们会竭尽全力阻止你这个擅闯黑塔的外来者。只有战胜他们，才可以继续往高处攀登。当然，战胜这些boss，你也将获得非常丰厚的奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/096ad8af9c4930561f23676869684d4d.poster.avif?t=1702712519\" width=796 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/096ad8af9c4930561f23676869684d4d.webm?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352120/extras/096ad8af9c4930561f23676869684d4d.mp4?t=1702712519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>好吧，在这里祝大家好运！",
